===========================
 IMP Development TODO List 
===========================

:Last update:   $Date: 2005/11/03 11:21:50 $
:Revision:      $Revision: 1.22.8.3 $
:Contact:       imp@lists.horde.org

In no particular order:

- Implement full mailbox caching in IMP_Mailbox::.

- Don't render large MIME parts.

- The folders page should be rendered by the Horde_Tree:: html renderer.

- Print all messages in a mailbox.

- Access readonly IMAP mailboxes.

- Add t-prot like features (http://freshmeat.net/articles/view/1235,
  http://www.escape.de/users/tolot/mutt/) for text massaging. Features we
  don't already have include: Remove mailing list footers; Shrink big
  quotations; Squeeze a sequence of blank lines to just two; Change a series
  of four or more periods or exclamation points into just three; Hide overlong
  signatures.

- Implement combinations of AND and OR rules in the IMP search screen.

- Allow thread sort in search results.
